                    {"id": 6, "question": "What was the practical application mentioned for bioluminescent compounds?", "options": ["Underwater lighting systems", "Deep-sea navigation", "Tracking cellular processes in biomedical research", "Commercial fishing lures"], "answer": "Tracking cellular processes in biomedical research", "explanation": "Green fluorescent protein became a tool for tracking cellular processes and monitoring gene expression."},
