                    {"id": 4, "question": "What did William Julius Wilson study?", "options": ["Global city networks", "Concentrated poverty in inner cities", "Factory worker productivity", "Suburban population growth"], "answer": "Concentrated poverty in inner cities", "explanation": "Wilson demonstrated how manufacturing job loss concentrated poverty in inner-city neighborhoods."},
